  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>Google</span> <span>2026-05-26 17:30</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42dab72d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FEs8kEaZbFVXYDia6mvpy6qZqEv9Tuia8RtCLPjpzJFZQqc6x9tJ7wtLJAv38pgoD5MjKVhHKlHTTOIDb3LoaVPJd8PnxoPTewQmqfRlUcJ8hA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>致谢所有提交反馈的朋友，用最真实的声音构建了 Gemma 4 更立体的形象。</p>\n  <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 8px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"504678286\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f31e66a9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FEs8kEaZbFVV1Y7qbVt6xpIqibE6qwwSF27Cyiby9elc58fLJQP5a9LM9UFCdYYfmcExwg2dzxPydcia9riaT2mAEsibcPL8T6IdUqctvjyjrqhbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemma 4 作为 Google 迄今为止最强大模型，凭借最高支持 256K 的超长上下文窗口、原生的文本与图像多模态理解，以及飙升的推理速度，无论是在专为手机端侧打造的小型模型 (E2B/E4B)，还是面向高吞吐推理的 26B MoE 架构，都把开源生态的科技向前推进了一大步。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了了解 Gemma 4 在实际场景中的效果，不久前，我们向大家发起了 Gemma 4 的使用体验调研，收到了大量热情响应。我们摘选出一些真实反馈，带大家看看最直观的 Gemma 4 落地体验！</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 90.042%;vertical-align: bottom;align-self: flex-end;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;align-self: stretch;margin: 0px;z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"transform: perspective(0px);-webkit-transform: perspective(0px);-moz-transform: perspective(0px);-o-transform: perspective(0px);transform-style: flat;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 0;transform: rotateX(180deg);-webkit-transform: rotateX(180deg);-moz-transform: rotateX(180deg);-o-transform: rotateX(180deg);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 45px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"504678285\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"svg\" data-w=\"45\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0da9423c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_svg%2FQ3auHgzwzM5plR7TQEwJv2N2jZ2fTCzJR9LJzOXjmYDCAjVbc4ZNpOc8LMMqn03EjSxiaSfXKUJVibChCgdciapD3joXX6XyAqBD5QzBgwX367EibgJk47UEYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dsvg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;margin: 0px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"transform: perspective(0px);-webkit-transform: perspective(0px);-moz-transform: perspective(0px);-o-transform: perspective(0px);transform-style: flat;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 0;transform: rotateX(180deg);-webkit-transform: rotateX(180deg);-moz-transform: rotateX(180deg);-o-transform: rotateX(180deg);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 45px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"svg\" data-w=\"45\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"504678284\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d001df8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_svg%2FQ3auHgzwzM6jOiaxwXmW1pn7ySmlYXXcPMicLibel6jTKrHpiaHicIt0RWQfoAvFkaElvDg253UKZsTLyvHfkxPNBibqictt4fdrCrZPwANuI58Q15vMCA7FMENhg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dsvg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);padding: 20px 10px;border-top-left-radius: 10px;border-top-right-radius: 10px;border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow-y: auto;height: 500px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;vertical-align: middle;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 Ch***ie</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"极其惊艳的是内置的 Thinking Mode (思维链推理)。在辅助我复习与备战考试时，它提供的逻辑拆解非常严密，能有效降低对复杂理论的理解成本。它的指令遵循能力很强，能完美适配我的终端环境，生成代码的风格也非常符合现代工程实践 (如 Python 3.12 的新特性支持)。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 bi****V2</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"我主要用 Gemma 4 处理直播录屏内容，提炼产品近期的热点话题和用户画像，辅助内容运营和投放策略制定。Gemma 4 在多模态理解上的表现让这类工作的效率有明显提升，过去需要人工看完整场直播才能总结的内容，现在可以快速拿到结构化的摘要和标签。期待后续在多语言直播场景 (如俄语、阿拉伯语、东南亚小语种等) 的理解能力上能持续加强，这对出海产品的本地化运营会非常有帮助。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 Je**me</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"这次体验 Gemma 4 整体感觉特别顺手，日常聊天、写文案、解答基础问题都很靠谱。理解指令特别精准，不用反复调整话术就能 get 到我的需求，回答逻辑清晰、条理分明。不管是简单日常咨询还是整理文案、梳理思路都能胜任，响应速度也很快，使用起来没有拖沓感，整体上手门槛低，普通人也能轻松用好，体验感很舒服。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 萍*</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"整体试用下来，Gemma 4 综合表现很亮眼，多轮对话体验很好，能顺着话题持续交流，不会轻易断逻辑。生成内容风格也很好把控，可正式可口语化，满足不同使用需求。端侧使用也很流畅，不用复杂设置就能直接用，对新手特别友好。小瑕疵很少，整体稳定性和智能性都在线，是日常高频使用很值得推荐的 AI 模型。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 zz**bs</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"Gemma 4 的代码生成能力确实超出了预期，特别是在编写数据处理、自动化分析脚本等任务时，逻辑清晰且几乎可以做到开箱即用，极大地提升了我的开发效率。同时，它对复杂 Prompt 的指令遵循度非常高，能够精准理解工程需求并给出符合预期的输出。作为一款开放权重的模型，目前的表现非常亮眼，未来会考虑将其集成到更多日常的研发工作流中。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 X-******vo</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"Gemma 4 给我的最大感受就是推理能力变强了，遇到数学计算、逻辑分析、规划类任务都处理得很到位。生成的内容不空洞，有实际参考价值，语言表达自然流畅，不会有生硬机器感。而且适配场景很全面，工作办公、学习答疑、生活闲聊都能兼顾，相比之前版本智能感提升明显，实用性特别强，日常办公帮了不少忙。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 Ry****ii</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"我们比较欣赏 Gemma 4 在端侧部署方面的开放性。通过 GGUF、llama.cpp、mmproj 等生态工具，可以在 Jetson 这类边缘算力设备上搭建本地推理服务，实现不依赖云端的 AI 能力，这对于工业场景非常重要，因为很多现场数据涉及隐私、安全和合规要求，不能轻易上传到云端。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 Op****21</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"模型在自然语言理解和生成方面展现出了相当高的水准，能够准确把握用户的意图，尤其在创意写作、内容总结和逻辑分析等任务上表现出色。与前代模型相比，Gamma 4 在上下文保持能力上有了显著提升，在长对话中依然能保持较高的连贯性和一致性。模型的回复风格自然流畅，具备良好的语感，整体交互体验比较人性化。对于日常办公、内容创作和学习辅助等使用场景，Gamma 4 能够提供切实有效的帮助，综合来看是一款值得推荐的 AI 模型产品。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 18px;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px -13px;border-radius: 7px;overflow: hidden;z-index: 1;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(59, 107, 255) 0%, rgb(46, 150, 255) 68%, rgb(129, 131, 236) 100%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n               <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@微信用户 Mi*****ng</span></strong></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgb(238, 246, 255);border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-bottom-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);padding: 15px 10px;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;border-radius: 17px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"整体体验是积极的。Gemma 4 在边缘设备上的表现相比以往小模型有明显提升，尤其是回答准确度、理解能力和日常任务完成质量都有进步，E2B、E4B 这类小模型的优势是可以在手机端本地运行，响应方便，隐私性和离线可用性较好，但目前仍需要进一步优化稳定性，尤其是避免 &lt;think&gt; 死循环；另外，E2B、E4B 更适合日常电脑本地部署，在速度和质量之间平衡较好，回答质量明显高于更小参数模型，同时本地运行体验也比较流畅。整体来看 Gemma 4 对本地 AI 和边缘 AI 的实用性提升很明显。\"</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: bottom;align-self: flex-end;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;background-color: rgb(25, 25, 25);border-top-right-radius: 10px;border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;overflow: hidden;padding: 5px 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 13px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.2;letter-spacing: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"display: inline-block;width: 1em;margin: 0px 0.2em;float: right;clear: none;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">向上滑动查看更多</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">篇幅有限，还有许多同样精彩的反馈无法在此一一展示。由衷感谢为我们提供宝贵反馈的每一位朋友，让技术不再只是冰冷的数据。因为有无数真实用户在不断试错、反馈、调优，才共同构成了 AI 生态向前演进的蓬勃动力，让我们对 Google AI 整个开放生态的未来演进充满了期待。欢迎您持续关注 Google AI！</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"43\" data-backw=\"578\" data-ratio=\"0.075\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=095c6e9f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrFWVXwibLGtz8OGvWKfTib36xjRAc6tFCNzVVPJhwuBnoV2j8GXYpytVWJa2FCZjylGsNgG6LiaiasHIbmJlKhASrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"402\" data-backw=\"578